===Noun===
'''[[video]] [[game]]''' (''plural'' '''video games''')
#A style of [[game]] existing as and controlled by [[software]], usually run by a [[video game console]] or a [[computer]], and played on a [[video terminal]] or [[television]] screen.  Controlled by a [[paddle]], [[joystick]], [[mouse]], cursor keys or a combination of any of these [[input devices]].

